Package: xray-vpn
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: systemd
Maintainer: Gleb Ivanov <realglebivanov@gmail.com>
Description: Xray TUN VPN with automatic route management
 Single daemon embedding xray-core with TUN mode.
 Fetches Russian IP ranges at startup, injects routing rules,
 manages fwmark-based split routing via netlink.
 Control: xray-vpn start|stop|status
